  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The PRstage LED BEAM 200 RING is a compact and powerful 200W moving head designed for professional applications. With its advanced optical system, it delivers up to 119,000 lux at 5 meters with a sharp 2° beam angle, making it ideal for concerts, clubs, tours, and stage events. The fixture features motorized focus, a color wheel with 13 vibrant colors plus open, and a fixed gobo wheel with 13 patterns. Its 48-facet rotating prism, frost filter, and rainbow effect expand creative possibilities. The integrated RGB LED ring offers additional visual effects with macros and strobe functions. Smooth 16-bit Pan/Tilt movement (540°/270°) ensures precise positioning, while the intuitive LCD display provides easy control. Operable via 24 DMX channels with RDM support, the unit is equipped with PowerCON and 3-pin XLR connections. With a lightweight 9.5 kg design, the LED BEAM 200 RING combines brightness, versatility, and reliability for modern lighting productions.",
